{"tid":2195194,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"（白吃白）警長涉詐騙警察儲蓄互助社貸款60萬賭外圍馬","createTime":"2020-09-09T04:21:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T09:23:25.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bed2b8f8427005194d3ae37bc1f81d87f1f8c466","tid":2195194,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T04:21:25.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】一名警長涉嫌詐騙警察儲蓄互助社貸款約六十萬元，以及投注非法外圍賭博，案件押後至12月再提堂。<br />\n<br />\n51歲的被告李鴻發抵達法院，他被控四項欺詐罪。<br />\n<br />\n案情指他1988年加入警隊，同年起成為警察儲蓄互助社社員；2008年晉升為警長，涉嫌2016年至2019年間向香港警察儲蓄互助社，訛稱在銀行或其他財務機構並無貸款，以及四份貸款申請表所載的資料完整和真確，意圖詐騙四筆貸款共六十萬元。<br />\n<br />\n他亦被控2020年向案中另一名被告余泉堅投注約2300元本地賽馬，涉嫌參與非法外圍賭博，兩人准以2千元保釋，12月2日再提堂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=404891\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D404891&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg84e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=8fecac09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D404891&h=b0f126bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=404891</a>"},{"pid":"40b099189105d5620b5e20322eff0f786d099d03","tid":2195194,"uid":54800,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T08:43:04.000Z","msg":"兩人准以2千元保釋!!!!<br />\n<br />\n鬆手到呢~~~<br />\nbtw ,詐騙警長停左職未.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96009a1c306a50cf94a35337606ed54b40214dac","tid":2195194,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:22:09.000Z","msg":"而家唔做世界等幾時先 ?   <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56953e6e3869fc1484cb2497a8d640d0443dfdad","tid":2195194,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:23:25.000Z","msg":"賭馬賭六十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}